snippet.title: A Tale of Two Kingdoms Playthrough 1
snippet.description:
The introduction.

Keep in mind this is NOT a PERFECT playthrough.  You won't get to see all the cut 
scenes so no griping about that.  This shows you the best way through most of the game.
